      "title_ko": null,
      "title_zh": null,
      "content_ko": "I have never seen an idol who truly cares for their fans like you do. Thank you so much for taking the time to chat with us every day despite your busy schedule, and for putting so much effort into organizing so many activities. Whenever I face difficulties, I think about how you overcome challenges in your singing career, and it feels like you’re right there with me, helping me through tough times. 감사합니다, 사랑해요!🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽❤️❤️❤️",
      "content_zh": "我从未见过像你这样真正关心粉丝的偶像。非常感谢你在繁忙的日程中每天抽时间与我们聊天，费心安排这么多活动。每当我遇到困难时，就会想到你在歌唱事业中如何克服挑战，感觉你就在我身边，帮助我度过难关。谢谢，我爱你！🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽❤️❤️❤️",
